{"tid":1401893,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"每次發夢 連登只有一個用途就係提供資訊 絕對唔係譴責","createTime":"2019-08-03T15:18:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T16:51:04.000Z","uid":83627,"like":81,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"ed1ea55e1eaf0926b857cb0e3862fa4bc9da6fb0","tid":1401893,"uid":83627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:18:44.000Z","msg":"如題 <br />\n冷氣軍師只需要講邊度有狗 邊度要人<br />\n譴責佢地 只有在場既人有資格<br />\n你地只不過係用關心佢地 戰略等等黎包裝你地既譴責<br />\n<br />\n既然前線決定留 佢地就預咗會俾人拉<br />\n當留守已經係<span style=\"color: red;\">既定事實</span><br />\n冷氣軍師應該係諗吓點樣係呢個<span style=\"color: red;\">既定事實</span>下完成目的（避免俾人拉）<br />\n<br />\n因為留守 已經成立 <br />\n所以唔好淨係講 早啲走咪無事 等等風涼說話"},{"pid":"53550fe586aa798254d2b785e1b56e3f9d8b47e3","tid":1401893,"uid":83627,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:21:19.000Z","msg":"星期一（5/8）罷工"},{"pid":"f23d35340fcf9470d1bc04aba347f1d4d878f7db","tid":1401893,"uid":83627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:21:45.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"31d79a4df794bb8fc9bc18ac2bf39e4e4cf45f74","tid":1401893,"uid":83627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:22:43.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"cf150f1f5bb5d03910089b46cbde98dbb4a321b3","tid":1401893,"uid":83627,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:23:22.000Z","msg":"5大訴求 缺一不可"},{"pid":"79de9116141931ffaa8c357f0884a425ef113368","tid":1401893,"uid":83627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:23:56.000Z","msg":"香港警察 知法犯法"},{"pid":"98041767879d8da42dbd99b69a1aedd28fefbc7b","tid":1401893,"uid":83627,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:24:16.000Z","msg":"香港警察 狗屎垃圾"},{"pid":"f08f947179818caf96b384c059dd8b48de7be2da","tid":1401893,"uid":29381,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:24:34.000Z","msg":"人地拎自已前途企上前線<br />\n你可以唔支持/唔理解佢地既做法<br />\n但唔該俾番D尊重 語氣唔該溫和少少 <br />\n除左佢地老豆老母無人有資格鬧佢地<br />\n<b